{"id":86997,"type":6,"name":"Dark Blue Season 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/03/e6/86997_uuIJX.jpg","summary":"　　Carter Shaw（Dylan McDermott）领导几个警官从事绝密的卧底工作。他们把自己的任务掩盖得天衣无缝，绝大多数同事都不知道他们在干什么。为了对抗犯罪分子，Shaw失去了妻子，也失去了过去的生活，这让他很受伤。一个人一旦有心事，人格就会出现缺陷－－《Saving Grace》中的Grace、《In Plain Sight》中的Mary都是如此，Shaw也不例外。 \r\n　　Shaw的队友包括刚刚新婚的警察Ty（Omari Hardwick），在「卧底行动」和「个人感情」上左右为难；行事鲁莽的Dean（Logan Marshall-Green），有时因为做得过火，导致队友们怀疑他「已经叛变」；初出茅庐的巡警Jaimie（Nicki Aycox），加入这个小队的唯一理由是她拥有极佳的撒谎天赋。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>深蓝 第一季</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/41033\">Michael Biehn</a>、<a href=\"/person/33118\">Tricia Helfer</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>July 15, 2009</li><li><span>结束: </span>September 16, 2009</li><li><span>类型: </span>罪案</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TNT</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1319636</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"TNT","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":335899,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335899","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335900,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335900","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335901,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335901","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335902,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335902","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335903,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335903","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335904,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335904","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":335905,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/335905","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"",